# ✅ **`.gitignore` for Full-Stack Project**

This covers:
✔ Node  
✔ Python  
✔ Vite/React  
✔ Virtual Envs  
✔ Logs  
✔ Builds  
✔ OS junk files  

Create **one `.gitignore` in root**:

```gitignore
# -------------------------
# Node / Frontend
# -------------------------
node_modules/
dist/
.next/
out/
npm-debug.log*
yarn-debug.log*
yarn-error.log*
pnpm-debug.log*
.vscode/

# dotenv
.env
.env.local
.env.production
.env.development

# -------------------------
# Python / Backend
# -------------------------
__pycache__/
*.pyc
*.pyo
*.pyd
*.pdb

# Virtual environments
venv/
ENV/
env/
.venv/

# FastAPI auto-generated
*.log

# -------------------------
# OS / Editor Files
# -------------------------
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
.idea/
*.swp
*.swo

# -------------------------
# Build / Output
# -------------------------
build/
uploads/
cache/
tmp/
